    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-12-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-12-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="443"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d443">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">858.9111 RR/43.12.02: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Sweden</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Stockholm</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-02">December 2,
                            1943</date>.<lb/>[Received December 3—7:08 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3908. Swedish politics. Our 3899.<note n="40" xml:id="d443fn40">Not
                        printed.</note> Swedish Foreign Office announces today Foreign Minister
                    Guenther yesterday made the following <hi rend="italic">démarche</hi> German
                    Minister Stockholm: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Swedish Government learns with greatest concern of measures against
                            students, teachers, Oslo University. It cannot refrain from making
                            urgent request measures be stopped especially announced intention deport
                            students. In interest continued Swedish-German relations, Government
                            appeals German Government comply with deeply felt desire Swedish
                            people.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
